I'm going to freeze to death.

12
00:05:57,720 --> 00:06:00,990
- 好了 好了 - 也许有人把锁换了．
-Okay, okay. -Well, maybe somebody changed the lock.

13
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:03,510
谁？是谁把锁换掉了呢？
Like who? Who's gonna change this lock?

14
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,740
噢,我也不知道. 我只是瞎猜的
Well, I don't know. It was just a suggestion.

15
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:09,190
噢,成了
Ah. Success.

16
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:11,350
瞧
Voila.

17
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,870
对了,就是这里
Well, this is it--

18
00:06:15,130 --> 00:06:17,070
