and get it feeling like a home.

23
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,150
你在这儿呆了多久呢？
How long since you were here?

24
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,750
噢,最美好的十年,在此度过
Oh, the better part of 10 years.

25
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:44,070
