I wanted to sell it after the old lady died,

26
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:46,190
但我弟弟弗兰克不同意.
but I couldn't get Frank to agree.

27
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:49,110
我想他需要个 避风港之类的地方
I guess he needed a hideout or something.

28
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:53,470
你能来看看这个吗？
Would you look at this?

29
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,230
别担心
And don't worry,

30
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:59,700
对我来说这些没有半点意义
this stuff means nothing to me.

31
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,190
已是过去了
It all goes.

32
00:07:01,290 --> 00:07:03,620
我想半数家产属于你兄弟的吧
I thought half of it was your brother's.

33
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:06,710
他只知道浪费光阴 真是不成才, 另外...
I've never known him to kick cash out of bed. Besides...

34
00:07:07,770 --> 00:07:10,410
他可能正在什么酒吧大醉酩酊呢
he's probably behind bars someplace.

35
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:11,980
你得知道
You know...

36
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:17,190
在我们对它整理前, 得让克里斯蒂看看这个地方
we have to let Kirsty see this place before we do a thing to it.

37
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,150
她会喜欢
She'll love it.

38
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,030
你真的想搬到这儿来吗？
You really want to move in here?

39
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,510
