我想这比布鲁克林好多了
I suppose it's better than Brooklyn.

41
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,950
噢,别开始,朱莉娅.
Oh, don't start, Julia.

42
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:30,500
