等等,我以为你暂时 会跟我们住一起
Wait, I thought you were going to stay with us for a while

66
00:09:35,370 --> 00:09:35,870
爸爸
Dad.

67
00:09:36,160 --> 00:09:37,550
你会喜欢这所房子.
Well, you'd like this house.

68
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,750
你会喜欢我的房子的
You'd like my room.

69
00:09:56,700 --> 00:09:59,580
我真的很想让你来 看看这房子.真的很棒
I'd really like you to see this house. It's something else.

70
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:01,990
也许在接下来的几天中 我会找份工作
Maybe in the next couple of days. I gotta find myself a job.

71
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,830
为什么呢？甜心
What for, sweetie?

72
00:10:03,920 --> 00:10:06,910
我说你架子摆够了吧, 没必要这样
Look, you've already made the gesture, there's no need--

73
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:09,790
爸,不是摆架子, 这是我必须做的事情
Dad, this isn't a gesture. This is something I need to do.

74
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:13,350
稍微信任我一下吧,好吗？
Come on and trust me a little, okay?

75
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:33,830
明天给我回电话 我会的,我会去见你
-Call me tomorrow. -I will. I'll see you.

76
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:36,150
再见了,爸爸
Bye, Dad.

77
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:00,300
你觉得怎么样？
So?

78
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:03,510
为什么不搬进来呢？
Why not?

79
00:11:04,510 --> 00:11:06,310
太棒了.
Great.

80
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,670
我们会在周日搬进来
We'll move in on Sunday.

81
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:13,470
听着,通过这个地方时 不能碰坏了它的表面
Listen, look out for the moulding on the way through here.

82
00:11:13,560 --> 00:11:15,990
- 好的 - 好的
- All right. - All right.

83
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:18,670
- 你能向后拉下吗？ - 当然
- Are you all right back there? -Yeah yeah.

84
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:22,780
对.好了.直接把它搬到楼上去
All right, okay. Now just take it straight up the stairs.

85
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:26,750
别担心.可以通过去
Don't worry, it'll get through.

86
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:29,590
- 好的．什么情况？ - 夹着我的手臂了！
-All right. What's the matter? -Hey, you got my arm!

87
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,670
好的 好的
- All right, all right. -Oh, God.

88
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,270
当心
-(Man)Watch it. -(Larry)Oh.

89
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:37,230
我们休息一下吧,伙计们
Let's take five, guys.

90
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,550
你那儿收拾的怎么样了？
How's things in there?

91
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,500
房间里像掉进了炸弹一样乱七八糟
Looks like a bomb dropped.

92
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,250
有啤酒吗？
You got any beer?

93
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:47,050
冰箱里有一些
There's some in the fridge.

94
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:50,430
噢,不错
Oh, well...

95
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:53,990
为什么不拿些啤酒来喝呢？
why don't I get it?

96
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:57,910
对我来说,没有比这更爽的事儿了
I've got nothing better to do.

97
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:06,320
抱歉打扰一下
Excuse me.

98
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:08,630
- 真是幸运的一天喔． - 嘿
-My lucky day. -Hi.

99
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:12,500
- 你想买张床吗？ - 不是很想
-Do you wanna buy a bed? -Not much.

100
00:13:12,640 --> 00:13:13,700
爸爸！
Dad?

101
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:15,110
- 克里斯蒂 - 嘿！
- Kirsty! -Hi.

102
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,110
哈罗,甜心,到这儿来
Hello, sweetie. Come here.

103
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:19,950
- 你们先歇会儿． - 噢 好的
-Here you go. -(Man)Oh, great.

104
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,390
这房子真大.
This is a big house.

105
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:23,940
- 你喜欢吗？ - 是的
-You like? -Yeah.

106
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:25,550
我喜欢
Me like.

107
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:28,790
如果我们能把这该死的床搬过去 我愿意带你参观一番
Ill give you the grand tour if we ever get this goddamn bed moved.

108
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:31,260
- 朱莉娅在这儿吗？ - 她在楼上
-Is Julia here? -She's upstairs.

109
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,430
注意,对她温和点儿,好吗？
Look, be gentle with her, okay?

110
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:36,510
- 她讨厌搬家． - 真让人惊讶
-She hates moving. -Surprise.

111
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:39,990
- 克里斯蒂． - 好啦 我会乖点
-Kirsty. -Okay, all right. I'll be nice.

112
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,310
你们继续做这累人的活儿吧
You get on with the grunt work

113
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:44,650
- 我得喝点儿咖啡． - 好主意
-and I'll make myself some coffee. -That's a great idea.

114
00:13:44,650 --> 00:13:46,390
- 厨房在那儿． - 好的
-There's the kitchen. -Okay.

115
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,990
再见
Bye.

116
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:52,830
那是你女儿吗？
-Is that your daughter? -Uh-huh.

117
00:13:52,920 --> 00:13:55,590
- 很像她妈妈． - 她妈妈已经过世了
-Got her mother's looks. -Her mother's dead.

118
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,060
拜托！
Come on.

119
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:14,430
噢 该死
Oh, shit.

120
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:18,560
我可以进来吗？
Can I come in?

121
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,350
我可以进来吗？
Can I come in?

122
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:31,290
- 你是朱莉娅 对吗？ - 没错
-You're Julia, right? -That's right.

123
00:14:32,090 --> 00:14:33,880
你是哪位？
Who are you?

124
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,590
我是弗兰克
I'm Frank.

125
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,910
我是你丈夫的兄弟.
I'm brother Frank.

126
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:42,470
噢,对
Oh, yes!

127
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:46,030
我...我是来参加婚礼的
I--I came for the wedding.

128
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,080
那,我可以进来了吗？
Well, can I come in or not?

129
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:54,310
对不起,当然可以
I'm sorry. Of course.

130
00:14:57,800 --> 00:14:59,390
热烈欢迎．
You're very welcome.

131
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:01,990
噢,听你这么说,我很欣慰
Yeah. Well, that's nice to know.

132
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:06,890
你有毛巾吗？
Do you have a towel?

133
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:09,910
你有毛巾吗？
Have you got a towel?

134
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,280
克里斯蒂！
Kirsty.

135
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:14,830
浴室里有一条
There's one in the bathroom.

136
