顺便说一句 爸爸有没有告诉你 我已经找到房子了呢？
Oh, by the way, did Daddy tell you I got a room?

137
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:21,320
房间不大,但挺好.
It's not that big, but it's okay.

138
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,580
朱莉娅
Julia?

139
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:29,270
朱莉娅
Julia?

140
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:18,150
我们喝点什么呢？
What shall we drink to?

141
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:22,950
结婚幸福么？
Wedded bliss?

142
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,790
我很幸福.
I'm very happy

143
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:28,190
噢,我相信
I'm sure you are.

144
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:32,310
你得让我吻新娘子
You're gonna let me kiss the bride?

145
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:49,400
拉里怎么办呢？
What about Larry?

146
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:59,040
忘了他
Forget him.

147
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:43,270
朱莉娅...朱莉娅...朱莉娅..
Julia... Julia... Julia...

148
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:03,070
你得替我分担点重力 我的脚被束住了.
I need to take the weight away from me, my foot's caught.

149
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,830
- 你明白吗？ - 明白了
-You got it? -I got it.

150
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:07,520
当我拉的时候,你在后面推一下
Now just push it to me as I pull.

151
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:36,150
这远远不够
It's never enough.

152
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:42,500
朱莉娅
Julia. Jul...

153
00:18:47,610 --> 00:18:49,190
拜托
Please.

154
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:56,190
我愿为你做任何事
Ill do anything you want.

155
00:18:58,880 --> 00:19:00,590
任何事
(Whispers) Anything.

156
00:19:11,630 --> 00:19:12,750
这儿
Here.

157
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:16,270
伤口很深吗？
Oh, is it deep?

158
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:18,190
不知道,我没有看
I don't know. I haven't looked.

159
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:19,990
你知道我怕血.
You know me and blood.

160
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:22,810
- 我快晕倒了． - 你不会晕倒
-I'm gonna faint. -You're not going to faint.

161
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,430
他妈的
Oh, shit!

162
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:27,990
- 让我看看 - 他妈的．
-Let me see. -Shit!

163
00:19:28,730 --> 00:19:31,150
得去医院缝几针
Oh, it's going to need stitches.

164
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:34,550
- 但我都快呕吐了． - 你不能吐
-I'm gonna throw up. -You're not going to throw up.

165
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:37,030
- 放松点儿．放松点儿 - 我都快呕吐了．
-Just take it easy, just take it easy. -I'm gonna throw up.

166
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:39,190
不会有事儿
It's going to be all right

167
00:19:39,320 --> 00:19:41,990
让我送你去医院
Let's get you to the hospital.

168
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:44,710
我真是太笨了
So stupid.

169
00:20:03,280 --> 00:20:05,030
怎么啦？
What happened?

170
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:07,030
只是个小意外.他没事了
It was just an accident. He's all right.

171
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:09,190
我说,你来开车好吗？ 得去医院给他缝几针
Look, will you drive? He needs stitches.

172
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:12,320
- 当然可以． - 车钥匙在厨房里
-Yeah, sure. -The keys are in the kitchen.

173
00:20:12,730 --> 00:20:15,460
- 我太笨了． - 不会有事儿
-So stupid. - It's all right.

174
00:22:43,710 --> 00:22:46,310
不不,我真不是开玩笑
No no, I am not kidding.

175
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,990
当时那个医生正在四处闲逛....
This doctor is poking around

176
00:22:48,080 --> 00:22:50,750
就像纳粹集中营里的军医 看见犯人一样兴奋
with all the delicacy and compassion of Josef Mengele,

177
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:52,710
我警告他: 听着 我要晕过去了喔！
and I'm warning him, : Listen, I'm gonna pass out

178
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:55,360
他说,噢！你当然不会,老兄
He says, Oh no, of course you're not, old boy. Of course you're not

179
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:57,550
接下来我倒在地面上...
The next thing you know, I'm on the floor

180
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,940
他傻站在那儿, 好像他才是需要帮助的人
and he's standing there like he's the one who needs help.

